Studio Ghibli style illustration of an ancient, weathered stone well in a moonlit forest clearing, with countless glowing paper lanterns of different colors floating upward from its depths into a star-filled indigo sky. Each lantern carries a soft inner light, creating a warm constellation against the cool night. Twisted old trees with gnarled roots frame the scene, their leaves catching the golden glow. A small figure in a flowing cloak stands at the well's edge, head tilted upward in wonder, watching the wisdom rise. Fireflies dance among tall grass and wildflowers. The atmosphere is contemplative and magical, suggesting the timeless gathering and sharing of knowledge across generations.
